    IndexedTraverserSet.VertexIndexedTraverserSet

    public class IndexedTraverserSet<S,I>
extends TraverserSet<S>
    A TraverserSet that has an index back to the object in the Traverser. Using this extension of TraverserSet can make it easier to find traversers within the set if the internal value is known. Without the index the entire TraverserSet needs to be iterated to find a particular value.
